  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed mansard roof extension, by reason of its inappropriate design, scale, bulk, massing and height is considered to form a discordant and dominant visual feature when seen from the surrounding public and private realm. The proposed development would dominate the front and rear roofline pertaining to the host building and cause visual harm whilst undermining the existing uniform and rhythmic roofline within the host terrace. It would therefore be contrary to policies CS8 (Enhancing Islington's Character) of Islington's Core Strategy 2011, Policy DM2.1 (design) of Islington's Development Management Policies 2013 and Islington's Urban Design Guide 2017."
